      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation study performed at 2.1M, 5.8M, and 14.3M cells. GCI for normalized index of hemolysis = 3.7% (fine-to-medium) and 4.2% (medium-to-coarse). Fine mesh (14.3M cells) adopted for all production runs. Wall y+ < 5 maintained on all blade surfaces."
    },
