      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) and relative hemolysis index (RH) are the regulatory-accepted metrics for CPB device hemolysis assessment. Both QoIs extracted directly from CFD shear stress and exposure time fields using the Giersiepen power-law model. RH < 1 acceptance criterion aligns with predicate device comparison framework."
