      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — same device class and flow regime as COU device. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB envelope. Blood analog fluid properties within 8% of whole blood viscosity. Geometric differences between validation and COU pump quantified; impeller tip clearance is the primary morphological difference and is bounded by the parametric sweep."
