      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; turbulence model selection justified by literature precedent for similar pump geometries.",
      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on published FDA pump CFD literature demonstrating superior near-wall performance for rotating machinery hemolysis prediction. Formal model form uncertainty analysis not required at MRL 2; literature justification accepted."
