    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Validation results demonstrate hemolysis index prediction within 8.3% of experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. UQ was performed and uncertainty ranges for key inputs are documented in the model inputs factor record, including reference to an internal screening sensitivity study that identified dominant drivers. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met with margin at all COU operating conditions. The assessment team finds sufficient credibility evidence to support regulatory submission for Class II CPB device 510(k) comparison.",
